---
[v1] arm64: dts: mediatek: enable watchdog for MT7986a-RFB

Enable watchdog device for MT7986a reference board to provide system
watchdog functionality.

Enabling the watchdog is required for proper operation of the WiFi
driver, as it uses the watchdog as a reset controller.
---
v1: Initial watchdog support for MT7986a-RFB.
---

--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/mt7986a-rfb.dts
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/mt7986a-rfb.dts
@@ -297,6 +297,10 @@
 	status = "okay";
 };
 
+&watchdog {
+	status = "okay";
+};
+
 &wifi {
 	status = "okay";
 	pinctrl-names = "default", "dbdc";
